def test_ipv4(self):
        ticket = text_(
            'b3e7156db4f8abde4439c4a6499a0668f9e7ffd7fa27b798400ecd'
            'ade8d76c530000000auserid!'
        )
        result = self._callFUT('secret', ticket, '198.51.100.1', 'sha256')
        self.assertEqual(result, (10, 'userid', [''], ''))
